---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';


import Icon from '../../../components/Icon.astro';

const city = "Tuscumbia";
const state = "Alabama";
const phone = "256-826-1100";

// Tuscumbia and Quad Cities neighborhoods
const neighborhoods = [
  "Downtown Tuscumbia",
  "Spring Park Area",
  "Ivy Green District",
  "North Commons",
  "East Tuscumbia",
  "West Tuscumbia",
  "Colbert Heights",
  "Spring Creek",
  "Cherokee",
  "Leighton",
  "Littleville",
  "Wilson Lake Area"
];

// What's included in deep cleaning
const includedServices = [
  "All surfaces dusted top to bottom",
  "Ceiling fans & light fixtures cleaned",
  "Baseboards thoroughly wiped",
  "Door frames & doors cleaned",
  "Window sills & tracks detailed",
  "All switch plates & outlets wiped",
  "Kitchen deep cleaned & degreased",
  "Inside oven cleaning",
  "Inside refrigerator cleaning",
  "Inside microwave & dishwasher",
  "Cabinet fronts cleaned",
  "All bathrooms deep scrubbed",
  "Tile grout cleaned",
  "Shower doors descaled",
  "Toilets sanitized inside & out",
  "Mirrors & glass polished",
  "Floors vacuumed & mopped",
  "Under furniture cleaned",
  "Trash removed & liners replaced"
];

// Process steps
const processSteps = [
  {
    step: "1",
    title: "Request Your Quote",
    description: "Tell us about your Tuscumbia home—square footage, number of rooms, and any specific needs. We'll provide a detailed, no-obligation quote."
  },
  {
    step: "2",
    title: "Schedule Your Clean",
    description: "Pick a date that works for you. We offer flexible scheduling and can work around Helen Keller Festival, holiday events, and guest arrivals."
  },
  {
    step: "3",
    title: "Deep Clean Every Room",
    description: "Our trained team systematically cleans your entire home—inside appliances, behind furniture, and everywhere regular cleaning misses."
  },
  {
    step: "4",
    title: "Enjoy Your Spotless Home",
    description: "Walk into a fresh, sanitized home that's ready for guests, family events, or simply your own enjoyment. Many clients continue with recurring service."
  }
];

// FAQs
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How much does deep cleaning cost in Tuscumbia?",
    answer: "Deep cleaning in Tuscumbia typically ranges from $225-$350 for average-sized homes (1,500-2,500 sq ft). Historic homes near Ivy Green or larger properties may run $325-$450+. Pricing depends on square footage, number of rooms, home condition, and specific requests. Call 256-826-1100 for a free quote."
  },
  {
    question: "What's included in deep cleaning vs. regular cleaning?",
    answer: "Deep cleaning goes far beyond regular maintenance. We clean appliance exteriors (oven, refrigerator, microwave), detail baseboards, clean window sills and tracks, degrease kitchen surfaces, deep scrub tile grout, clean under and behind furniture, dust ceiling fans and light fixtures, and sanitize high-touch surfaces throughout your Tuscumbia home."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you clean historic homes near Ivy Green?",
    answer: "Absolutely! Tuscumbia's historic homes—including beautiful 19th-century residences near Ivy Green and properties in the National Register Historic District—require specialized care. We use gentle, pH-neutral products that protect original hardwood floors, antique fixtures, and architectural details while delivering a thorough clean."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you clean before Helen Keller Festival events?",
    answer: "Yes! The Helen Keller Festival brings thousands of visitors to Tuscumbia each June, and many residents host out-of-town guests. We offer pre-event deep cleaning to get your home guest-ready, plus post-event cleaning to restore order. The same applies for 'It's a Dickens Christmas, Y'all' and other Tuscumbia festivals."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does deep cleaning take in Tuscumbia?",
    answer: "Typical Tuscumbia homes (1,500-2,500 sq ft) take 3-5 hours for thorough deep cleaning. Historic homes with detailed architectural features or larger properties may take 5-7+ hours. We don't rush—we ensure every area meets our standards before leaving."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you serve the entire Quad Cities area?",
    answer: "Yes! We serve all of the Shoals including Tuscumbia, Florence, Muscle Shoals, and Sheffield. Whether you're in downtown Tuscumbia near Spring Park, near Wilson Lake, or anywhere in Colbert County, we deliver professional service. Our familiarity with the Quad Cities means we understand each community."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you clean Wilson Lake vacation rentals?",
    answer: "Yes, we specialize in vacation rental cleaning for Wilson Lake properties and Tuscumbia Airbnbs. With year-round tourism attractions like Ivy Green, Alabama Music Hall of Fame, and The Miracle Worker performances, keeping your rental guest-ready is essential. We offer reliable turnover service to maintain your 5-star rating."
  },
  {
    question: "Should I start with deep cleaning before recurring service?",
    answer: "We highly recommend it. A deep clean establishes a pristine baseline, then recurring service maintains that level. Think of it like detailing your car before regular washes. Most Tuscumbia clients start with deep cleaning, then transition to biweekly or monthly service."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you approach original hardwood floors in historic Tuscumbia homes?",
    answer: "Historic Tuscumbia homes often have original tongue-and-groove hardwood floors from the late 1800s or early 1900s that require completely different care than modern flooring. We avoid excess moisture, use pH-neutral hardwood-safe cleaners, and never apply steam. We also dry-buff rather than wet-mop wherever possible. For homes near Ivy Green in the National Register Historic District, we err on the side of caution and confirm product compatibility before any floor treatment."
  },
  {
    question: "How often should a Tuscumbia home get a professional deep clean?",
    answer: "For most Tuscumbia households, a thorough deep clean twice per year — once in spring after pollen season and once in fall before the holiday entertaining season — keeps the home in excellent condition alongside regular maintenance cleaning. Households with pets, young children, or frequent guests may benefit from quarterly deep cleaning. Wilson Lake vacation rentals typically need deep cleaning at the beginning and end of peak season, plus mid-season if occupancy is high."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you deep clean before putting a home on the market?",
    answer: "Absolutely, and it's one of the highest-return investments a Tuscumbia seller can make before listing. Listing photos capture dust on ceiling fans, grime on kitchen surfaces, and water stains in bathrooms in ways you may not notice when living in the home. A professional deep clean before photography and showings creates a strong first impression that supports your asking price. We work with real estate agents and sellers throughout Colbert County and are familiar with the turnaround timelines listing processes require."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you bring your own cleaning products or use what I have?",
    answer: "We bring all professional-grade cleaning products and equipment to every job. For most Tuscumbia homes, our standard kit includes EPA-registered disinfectants, pH-neutral hardwood floor cleaner, grout-specific cleaning agents, degreaser formulas for kitchen surfaces, and glass-safe products for mirrors and windows. If you have specific preferences — fragrance-free products, particular brands, or concerns about specific surfaces — let us know when booking and we'll adjust accordingly."
  }
];

// Schema markup
const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Deep Cleaning Tuscumbia AL",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "name": "The Valley Clean Team",
    "telephone": "+12568261100",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "addressLocality": "Tuscumbia",
      "addressRegion": "AL",
      "addressCountry": "US"
    }
  },
  "areaServed": neighborhoods.map(n => ({
    "@type": "Place",
    "name": `${n}, Tuscumbia, AL`
  })),
  "serviceType": "Deep Cleaning",
  "description": "Professional deep cleaning services in Tuscumbia, Alabama. Comprehensive top-to-bottom cleaning for homes throughout Colbert County and the Shoals."
};

const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": faqs.map(faq => ({
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": faq.question,
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": faq.answer
    }
  }))
};
import BookingCTA from "../../../components/BookingCTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Deep Cleaning Tuscumbia AL | Valley Clean Team"
  description="Professional deep cleaning in Tuscumbia, AL. Serving Ivy Green area, Quad Cities, Wilson Lake. Inside appliances, baseboards. Veteran-owned."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-green-50 border border-green-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
            <span class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              <Icon name="sparkles" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Top-to-Bottom Cleaning
            </span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-6 leading-tight">
            Deep Cleaning Services in <span class="gold-gradient">Tuscumbia, Alabama</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
            From historic homes near Ivy Green to lakeside properties along Wilson Lake, our comprehensive deep cleaning service reaches every corner of your Tuscumbia home. We clean appliance exteriors, behind furniture, and everywhere regular cleaning misses—leaving your home truly, thoroughly clean.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Trust Badges -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
              <Icon name="medal" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Veteran-Owned</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
              <Icon name="shield-alt" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">$2M Insured</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
              <Icon name="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" fill="currentColor" />
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">130+ 5-Star Reviews</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Price -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-md border border-gray-100 inline-block mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Deep Cleaning From</span>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#FFA985]">$225</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-gray-300">|</div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Typical Homes</span>
                <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">$275-$350</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-gray-300">|</div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Historic/Larger</span>
                <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">$325-$450+</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- CTAs -->
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="#quote" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
              <Icon name="calendar-check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Get Free Quote
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+12568261100" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] bg-white border-2 border-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#FFA985]/10 transition-all">
              <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />{phone}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote Form -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2 text-center">Get Your Free Quote</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-6">The Shoals' trusted deep cleaning professionals</p>
          <BookingCTA city="Tuscumbia" variant="card" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Tuscumbia Homes Need Deep Cleaning -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-8">
          Why Tuscumbia Homes Need <span class="gold-gradient">Professional Deep Cleaning</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-6">
            Tuscumbia—birthplace of Helen Keller and heart of the Shoals—is a community steeped in history and Southern hospitality. From the beautiful 19th-century homes near Ivy Green to charming residences throughout downtown, Tuscumbia's architectural heritage requires thoughtful care. Regular cleaning simply can't address the dust that accumulates in historic trim, vintage fixtures, and high ceilings.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The Shoals area's Tennessee River location also creates unique challenges. Wilson Lake humidity, seasonal pollen, and Alabama's red clay soil all find their way into your home. For families hosting guests during Helen Keller Festival, The Miracle Worker performances, or holiday events, a deep clean ensures your home makes the impression you want.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you're preparing for festival season, recovering from hosting visitors, getting a vacation rental guest-ready, or simply haven't had time for thorough cleaning, our deep cleaning service addresses every area of your Tuscumbia home. We clean appliance exteriors, behind furniture, and in corners that daily cleaning misses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        What's Included in <span class="gold-gradient">Tuscumbia Deep Cleaning</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Comprehensive cleaning that goes far beyond regular maintenance
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        {includedServices.map((service) => (
          <div class="flex items-center bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">{service}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        Our <span class="gold-gradient">Deep Cleaning Process</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Systematic, thorough, and designed for Shoals area homes
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        {processSteps.map((step) => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white text-2xl font-bold">
              {step.step}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">{step.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Areas Served -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        Deep Cleaning Throughout <span class="gold-gradient">The Shoals</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Serving Tuscumbia, Florence, Muscle Shoals, Sheffield & Colbert County
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <!-- Tuscumbia -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4 flex items-center">
            <Icon name="landmark" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Tuscumbia
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Downtown Tuscumbia</li>
            <li>• Spring Park Area</li>
            <li>• Ivy Green District</li>
            <li>• North Commons</li>
            <li>• East & West Tuscumbia</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Colbert County -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4 flex items-center">
            <Icon name="home" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Colbert County
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Colbert Heights</li>
            <li>• Spring Creek</li>
            <li>• Cherokee</li>
            <li>• Leighton</li>
            <li>• Littleville</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quad Cities -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4 flex items-center">
            <Icon name="map-marked-alt" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Quad Cities
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Florence</li>
            <li>• Muscle Shoals</li>
            <li>• Sheffield</li>
            <li>• Wilson Lake Area</li>
            <li>• Tennessee River Properties</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-12">
        Why Shoals Families Choose <span class="gold-gradient">The Valley Clean Team</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="landmark" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Historic Home Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Tuscumbia's 19th-century homes deserve gentle care. We use pH-neutral products that protect original hardwood, antique fixtures, and architectural details.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="calendar-star" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Festival-Ready Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Helen Keller Festival, The Miracle Worker, Dickens Christmas—we help you prepare for hosting with pre-event deep cleaning and post-event restoration.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="water" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Wilson Lake Rentals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Vacation rental owners trust us for reliable deep cleaning and turnover service. We help maintain your 5-star rating with thorough, consistent cleans.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="medal" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Veteran-Owned</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Military precision and values you can trust. We approach every Shoals home with discipline, attention to detail, and commitment to excellence.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="shield-alt" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">$2M Insured</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Fully bonded and insured for your complete peace of mind. Your historic home and irreplaceable heirlooms are protected throughout our service.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="star" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" fill="currentColor" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Satisfaction Guaranteed</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">If you're not happy with any aspect of your deep clean, we'll come back and make it right. 130+ five-star reviews prove our commitment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Perfect For Section -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        When to Schedule <span class="gold-gradient">Deep Cleaning</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Deep cleaning is ideal for these situations
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <Icon name="users" class="w-5 h-5 text-3xl text-[#FFA985] mb-3" />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Before Guests Arrive</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Helen Keller Festival, Miracle Worker performances, holiday visitors—be guest-ready.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <Icon name="leaf" class="w-5 h-5 text-3xl text-[#FFA985] mb-3" />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Seasonal Refresh</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Spring cleaning, fall prep, or any time your home needs a comprehensive refresh.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <Icon name="key" class="w-5 h-5 text-3xl text-[#FFA985] mb-3" />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Vacation Rentals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Deep clean between guests or seasonal refresh for your Wilson Lake property.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <Icon name="sync-alt" class="w-5 h-5 text-3xl text-[#FFA985] mb-3" />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Before Recurring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Establish a pristine baseline before starting weekly or biweekly service.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local Expert Guide -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        Deep Cleaning in Tuscumbia: <span class="gold-gradient">A Local Expert Guide</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="section-divider mb-10"></div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>
          Tuscumbia sits at the intersection of two things that create accelerated cleaning needs in every home: Southern humidity and genuine historic housing stock. The Tennessee River and Wilson Lake system generates moisture levels that drive mildew growth in bathrooms, grout discoloration in kitchens, and a general heaviness in the air from late spring through September that regular cleaning cannot fully address. When that humidity is filtered through 19th-century window frames, Victorian-era plaster walls, and original hardwood floors with gaps between boards, the result is a cleaning environment that requires specific expertise. Homes near the Ivy Green National Register Historic District aren't just old — they're architecturally precious, and cleaning methods that work fine in modern construction can cause irreversible damage to period materials.
        </p>
        <p>
          Tuscumbia's event calendar creates a natural rhythm for deep cleaning that residents quickly learn to anticipate. The Helen Keller Festival each June transforms the downtown area and surrounding neighborhoods into a regional gathering point, with residents hosting out-of-town family and festival visitors who otherwise never make it to the Shoals. The Miracle Worker drama performances throughout the summer attract audiences to Ivy Green itself and bring a second wave of culturally-minded visitors who often stay with Tuscumbia locals. Dickens Christmas in December closes out the year with another major hosting occasion. The households that consistently impress guests during these events are the ones that deep clean before each major festival window rather than attempting to spot-clean when guests are already en route.
        </p>
        <p>
          Wilson Lake properties present their own deep cleaning logic. Lakeside homes and vacation rentals along the Wilson Lake shoreline accumulate a specific combination of challenges: red clay soil tracked in from the bank, algae and mineral deposits from watercraft cleaning near the house, higher humidity than comparable inland properties, and the wear pattern of guests who use the property hard during outdoor recreation and don't clean before departure. Seasonal deep cleaning — opening the property for the recreation season in spring and closing it down properly in fall — prevents the compounding buildup that makes mid-season cleaning exponentially harder. Wilson Lake rental owners who skip the seasonal deep clean often find themselves investing significantly more time and money restoring the property at the end of the year.
        </p>
        <p>
          The specific areas that most frequently need professional-level attention in Tuscumbia homes reflect the region's character. Alabama red clay is among the most stubborn soil types for flooring — it grinds into grout lines and light-colored hardwood finishes in ways that regular mopping cannot address without the right combination of cleaning agents and technique. Kitchen exhaust systems in the Shoals accumulate cooking grease faster in humid conditions. The space between kitchen appliances and adjacent walls, the undersides of bathroom vanities, and the interior of window AC units all collect debris that builds up invisibly until it becomes a genuine hygiene concern. Deep cleaning reaches all of these systematically rather than hoping a regular clean passes over them.
        </p>
        <p>
          Pre-listing deep cleaning is one of the highest-ROI services we provide for Tuscumbia homeowners. The Shoals real estate market has been consistently active, with Tuscumbia's relative affordability and quality of life drawing buyers from Huntsville and Birmingham who are willing to commute or work remotely. When a home goes to market, professional photography captures everything — including the grease on the stove hood, the soap scum in the master bath, and the dust on the ceiling fan blades above the dining table. A deep clean before listing photography isn't a vanity expense; it's a direct contributor to how quickly the home sells and at what price. We work with sellers on quick-turnaround pre-listing schedules throughout Colbert County.
        </p>
        <p>
          Many Tuscumbia households begin their relationship with us through a single deep clean — often before a major event, after purchasing a new home, or when recurring cleaning has lapsed for months. The common experience is that the deep clean produces a result so noticeably different from what they were maintaining on their own that transitioning to recurring service becomes an obvious choice. We structure the transition to make economic sense: the deep clean establishes a baseline, and then biweekly or monthly recurring service maintains that standard at a fraction of the cost of another deep clean from scratch. After years of working in the Shoals, we've seen this pattern repeat consistently — the deep clean is the beginning of a long-term relationship, not a one-time transaction.
        </p>
